    <name>SyncThingy</name>
    <developer_name>zocker_160</developer_name>
    <summary>SyncThingy = Synthing + simple tray indicator</summary>
    <description>
        <p>SyncThingy is a simple tray indicator for Syncthing written in C++.</p>
        <p>
        Following the KISS principle, it allows you to see if Syncthing is running, stop it and manage it using the default webui.
        </p>
    </description>

